title: Achieving Zero-Instrumentation Monitoring with eBPF
---

Metrics are powerful tools that exist in the cloud-native ecosystem using Prometheus. However, using facilities to enable monitoring requires instrumenting the code. Everyone wants observability, but nobody wants to go the extra mile to instrument their clusters or applications. This is where eBPF comes in...

